{"version":1,"entries":{"person_4462073_translations":{"at":1772469198782,"data":{"id":4462073,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"黄誉博","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Huang Yu Bo (黄誉博) is a Chinese singer.","name":"Huang Yubo","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"黃譽博","primary":false}}]}},"person_15170_translations":{"at":1772469199558,"data":{"id":15170,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"中国演员，毕业于北京电影学院表演系90级，在校期间担任班长。\n\n1999年，因电影《洗澡》中出演二明为人所知，并且凭借此片相继获得2000第7届北京大学生电影节最佳男演员奖、2000年第5届中国长春电影节最佳男配角奖等等总共四个奖项。\n\n1992年，代表作《葛老爷子》获中国长春国际电影节“长春银杯奖”。\n\n1999年，《美丽新世界》获得1999年第19届夏威夷国际电影节最佳男主角奖。\n\n2004年，《别了温哥华》获得2004年第四届电视节“双十佳”“十佳”演员奖。\n\n2007年，《5颗子弹》获得2007第26届中国电影金鸡奖最佳男配角提名。\n\n2009年，《我的唐朝兄弟》获得2010第6届中美电影节最佳男主角奖、2010第2届英国万像国际华语电影节最佳男演员奖。\n\n2009年，《满堂爹娘》获得2010年2010春季电视剧互联网盛典最佳男演员奖。\n\n2011年，《誓言今生》获得2012年第8届华鼎奖中国近代革命题材电视剧最佳男演员。\n\n2013年，主演贾樟柯导演电影《天注定》，此片入围第66届戛纳国际电影节正式竞赛单元，5月17日在戛纳全球首映，荣膺最佳编剧奖。\n\n2015年，姜武出任2015海峡国际微电影节形象大使。","name":"姜武","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Jiang Wu was born on November 14, 1967 in Tangshan, China. He has graduated from Beijing Film Academy.\n\nHe starred in Zhang Yimou's To Live (1994), and Zhang Yang's Shower (1999). He is the younger brother of director, screenwriter and actor Jiang Wen.","name":"Jiang Wu","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"姜武","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Khương Vũ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Jiang Wu","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"中國演員，畢業於北京電影學院表演系 90 級，在校期間擔任班長。\n\n1999 年，因電影《洗澡》中出演二明為人所知，並且憑藉此片相繼獲得 2000 第 7 屆北京大學生電影節最佳男演員獎、2000 年第 5 屆中國長春電影節最佳男配角獎等等總共四個獎項。\n\n1992 年，代表作《葛老爺子》獲中國長春國際電影節“長春銀盃獎”。\n\n1999 年，《美麗新世界》獲得 1999 年第 19 屆夏威夷國際電影節最佳男主角獎。\n\n2004 年，《別了温哥華》獲得 2004 年第四屆電視節“雙十佳”“十佳”演員獎。\n\n2007 年，《5 顆子彈》獲得 2007 第 26 屆中國電影金雞獎最佳男配角提名。\n\n2009 年，《我的唐朝兄弟》獲得 2010 第 6 屆中美電影節最佳男主角獎、2010 第 2 屆英國萬像國際華語電影節最佳男演員獎。\n\n2009 年，《滿堂爹孃》獲得 2010 年 2010 春季電視劇網際網路盛典最佳男演員獎。\n\n2011 年，《誓言今生》獲得 2012 年第 8 屆華鼎獎中國近代革命題材電視劇最佳男演員。\n\n2013 年，主演賈樟柯導演電影《天註定》，此片入圍第 66 屆戛納國際電影節正式競賽單元，5 月 17 日在戛納全球首映，榮膺最佳編劇獎。\n\n2015 年，姜武出任 2015 海峽國際微電影節形象大使。","name":"姜武","primary":false}}]}},"person_2025827_translations":{"at":1772469201407,"data":{"id":2025827,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Justin Gant","primary":true}}]}},"person_2252438_translations":{"at":1772469204229,"data":{"id":2252438,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"JYP엔터테인먼트 소속 5인조 걸그룹 ITZY의 멤버.\n\n2017년 Stray Kids와 믹스나인에 출연과 방탄소년단 LOVE YOURSELF Highlight Reel '起承轉結'에서 제이홉과 지민의 파트너 역으로 얼굴을 알렸고, 2019년 걸그룹 ITZY의 멤버로 데뷔했다.","name":"류진","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Shin Ryu-jin (신류진; born April 17, 2001), known professionally as Ryujin (류진) is a South Korean singer and actress under JYP Entertainment. She is a member of the South Korean girl group ITZY.","name":"Ryujin","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}}]}},"person_2720168_translations":{"at":1772469204334,"data":{"id":2720168,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Arm Weerayut Chansook is an actor, singer, model, MC and fashion designer under GMMTV. In 2015, he graduated with a bachelor's degree from the Faculty of Fine Arts at Srinakharinwirot University, majoring in Acting and Directing.\n\nIn 2007, Arm participated in the Luk Thung Star Contest where he placed as first runner-up. Later, he enrolled in a singing school. He started in the entertainment industry in 2010 as an artist under the record label RS Public Company Limited. With his singing and dancing abilities, he was selected as a member of Rookie BB, a boy band under the management of RS Music.\n\nIn 2016, Arm joined GMMTV where he made his acting debut with a supporting role in the series \"Senior Secret Love: Bake Me Love\". Representing his home county, he performed with his fellow GMMTV artist Amp Phurikulkrit Chusakdiskulwibul in South Korea during the 2018 DMC Festival, an annual event organized by Munhwa Broadcasting Corporation (MBC).\n\nAside his acting and singing career, Arm has become known for his fashion and styling skills through his lifestyle program \"Arm Share\". He owns two clothing brands: Homles and AWC. He's also the owner of AWC studio.","name":"Weerayut Chansook","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"วีรยุทธ จันทร์สุข","primary":true}}]}},"person_3356081_translations":{"at":1772469206173,"data":{"id":3356081,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Ma Yan (马岩) is a Chinese actor.","name":"Ma Yan","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english