ased project group JASP.ER under GMMTV and Riser Music. Born in Thailand, he moved to Türkiye at eight years old with his mother and stepfather and lived there until he was sixteen. Joong then came back to Thailand to finish his education. He changed his name a number of times before entering show business, including taking his stepfather's surname. He is currently studying broadcasting and streaming media production at Bangkok University's School of Communication Arts.\n\nHe made his acting debut in 2019 with a main role in the series \"2 Moons 2\".\n\nJoong was formerly a member of boy group \"OXQ\" under Motive Village and boy group \"Insight Rookies\" under Insight Entertainment. Joong has been an artist under GMMTV since September 2021. On December 19, 2024, he made his debut with Project JASP.ER with the release of their debut single \"Sadistic\".","name":"Archen Aydin","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"阿晨·艾丁","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Joong Archen Aydin","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"阿晨·艾丁","primary":false}}]}},"person_6018713_translations":{"at":1772469230995,"data":{"id":6018713,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Catherine McDonough","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Катрин МакДонаф","primary":false}}]}},"person_3607505_translations":{"at":1772469231281,"data":{"id":3607505,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Ren Watabe (born 6 March 1999) is a Japanese actor.","name":"Ren Watabe","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN"